    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit delivers exceptional linear power through its six independent throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS variable valve timing system. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul. The rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced to ensure long-term chassis rigidity. Suspension remains tight with refreshed bushings and OE-spec dampers, maintaining the car\u2019s legendary handling dynamics. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use consistent with its age, the drivetrain is robust and track-ready.",
      "price": 31500.0,
