      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle strikes the perfect balance between performance and daily practicality. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine with only minor cosmetic imperfections consistent with careful, respectful use. Inside, the cabin remains remarkably clean; the premium upholstery is free of tears, and every electronic feature\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, benefiting from a strict adherence to its service schedule, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of tires. It drives smoothly, shifts crisply, and offers a quiet, confident ride. This is a turn-key example for a buyer seeking a reliable, well-documented vehicle that shows true pride of ownership. Includes a full service history and both original key fobs.",
